nodes.text: Prixqip, known as Prixqip the Mutilator, was a criminal active during the Imperial Era. Prixqip was killed by the droid bounty hunter IG-88, who chose not to claim the bounty straight away. When IG-88 was captured by a criminal gang led by Kaluub Akjee, Prixqip was one of several bounties that Akjee attempted to claim from the Gillanium Syndicate.
